籤詩版本二:
Kunzima kakhulu ukuzabalazela impumelelo, kodwa iintsuku zokulwela umtshato zixakeke okwexeshana.
Ke yena uya kugetyengwa lutolo, Ingangamsha ikhokela amanene.
詩意:
Le hexagram imele intsikelelo efihliweyo.
Yonke into ilungile.
解曰: Ukutshintsha ngabom. Enron ekugqibeleni. Ukuba ubuza malunga nokusetyenziswa. Kuphela kufutshane nabantu abahloniphekileyo.
籤詩故事一:
◇Ingcebiso ngencwadi uJiang Wei (Incwadi ecetyiswa nguJiang Wei)
UJiang Wei (202-264), igama lembeko uBoyue, wayeyinzalelwane yaseJi County, kwiNqila yaseTianshui, eLiangzhou (ngoku eyiGangu County, isiXeko saseTianshui, kwiPhondo laseGansu).
Ngexesha loBukumkani obuThathu, u-Kong Ming wakhokela imikhosi yaseQishan izihlandlo ezithandathu ukuya kuhlasela iCao Wei. U-Kong Ming wayegula kakhulu kwaye wayekwimeko emaxongo. Ufundise izahluko ezingamashumi amabini anesine zeNcwadi yeMfazwe kuJiang Wei jikelele, ngethemba lokuba angalizuza ilifa lakhe.
(Umzekeliso weli bali kukuba uJiang Wei wazuzwa ngenxa yesizathu esithile)
聖意: Ithamsanqa losapho, ithamsanqa, ishishini, umtshato, Liujia, abahambi ngeenyawo abakafiki, Tiansi Zhongping, Liu izilwanyana zasekhaya, Zhongping, ufuna abantu, amatyala oluntu, imfuduko enesizathu, impahla elahlekileyo, izifo zaseMpuma, ingcwaba laseXingxingshan lilungile.
古人: Iingcebiso ngencwadi kuJiang Wei (Iincwadi eziya kuJiang Wei)
